#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.114"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.114:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.114:0.2"
msgid "12. Andhakavindavagga"
msgstr "12. At Andhakavinda"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.114:0.3"
msgid "114. Andhakavindasutta"
msgstr "114. At Andhakavinda"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.114:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā magadhesu viharati andhakavinde."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Magadhans at "
"Andhakavinda."

msgctxt "an5.114:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ "
"bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one "
"side. The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: samādapetabbā → samādāpetabbā (?)
msgctxt "an5.114:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye te, ānanda, bhikkhū navā acirapabbajitā adhunāgatā imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ, "
"te vo, ānanda, bhikkhū pañcasu dhammesu samādapetabbā nivesetabbā "
"patiṭṭhāpetabbā."
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, those mendicants who are junior, recently gone forth, newly come to "
"this teaching and training should be encouraged, supported, and established "
"in five things."

msgctxt "an5.114:2.2"
msgid "Katamesu pañcasu?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.114:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘Etha tumhe, āvuso, sīlavā hotha, pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvutā viharatha "
"ācāragocarasampannā aṇumattesu vajjesu bhayadassāvino, samādāya sikkhatha "
"sikkhāpadesū’ti—iti pātimokkhasaṃvare samādapetabbā nivesetabbā "
"patiṭṭhāpetabbā."
msgstr ""
"They should be encouraged, supported, and established in restraint in the "
"monastic code: ‘Reverends, please be ethical. Live restrained in the code of "
"conduct, accomplished in appropriate behavior and means of collecting alms. "
"Seeing danger in the slightest flaw, keep the rules you’ve undertaken.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: nipakkasatino → nepakkasatino (?)
msgctxt "an5.114:3.1"
msgid ""
"‘Etha tumhe, āvuso, indriyesu guttadvārā viharatha ārakkhasatino "
"nipakkasatino, sārakkhitamānasā satārakkhena cetasā samannāgatā’ti—iti "
"indriyasaṃvare samādapetabbā nivesetabbā patiṭṭhāpetabbā."
msgstr ""
"They should be encouraged, supported, and established in sense restraint: ‘"
"Reverends, please live with sense doors guarded, under mindful protection "
"and discipline, with protected mind, having a heart protected by "
"mindfulness.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.114:4.1"
msgid ""
"‘Etha tumhe, āvuso, appabhassā hotha, bhasse pariyantakārino’ti—iti "
"bhassapariyante samādapetabbā nivesetabbā patiṭṭhāpetabbā."
msgstr ""
"They should be encouraged, supported, and established in limiting their "
"speech: ‘Reverends, please speak little. Put a limit on your speech.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.114:5.1"
msgid ""
"‘Etha tumhe, āvuso, āraññikā hotha, araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevathā’ti—iti kāyavūpakāse samādapetabbā nivesetabbā patiṭṭhāpetabbā."
msgstr ""
"They should be encouraged, supported, and established in retreat: ‘"
"Reverends, please live in the wilderness. Frequent remote lodgings in the "
"wilderness and the forest.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.139"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.114:6.1"
msgid ""
"‘Etha tumhe, āvuso, sammādiṭṭhikā hotha sammādassanena samannāgatā’ti—iti "
"sammādassane samādapetabbā nivesetabbā patiṭṭhāpetabbā."
msgstr ""
"They should be encouraged, supported, and established in right perspective: ‘"
"Reverends, please hold right view and have right perspective.’"

msgctxt "an5.114:6.2"
msgid ""
"Ye te, ānanda, bhikkhū navā acirapabbajitā adhunāgatā imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ, te "
"vo, ānanda, bhikkhū imesu pañcasu dhammesu samādapetabbā nivesetabbā "
"patiṭṭhāpetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Those mendicants who are junior, recently gone forth, newly come to this "
"teaching and training should be encouraged, supported, and established in "
"these five things.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.114:6.3"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
